@cobu

Try the ed2k network for the maps. You can use a client like emule http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/emule/eMule0.48a-Installer2.exe.

The maps have prm extension. You copy these files to the system/apps/route66/maps folder of the memory card. If that folder does not exist, make it. All these instructions are in the guides.

Cheers

Carl@svane.se

@VX-man
I used an online translation service cuz i don't speak swedish. So bear with me if I mis understood.

You problem is most likely due to the .prm map file not being in the right directory. It should be in system/apps/route66/maps folder of your memory card. You cannot access the system folder via pcsuite or the inphone file manager. You have to use a card reader or the fexplore application. To copy the files to the right directory.
Read the guide carefully. Its all there. 
cheers. Merry Christmas to you too. :-)
